subpanels.description: Adult medusae of Olindias sambaquiensis Müller in oral view.
Umbrellar margin of Olindias sambaquiensis Müller with primary tentacles inserted on exumbrela, and secondary tentacles and club-shaped protrusions originating on umbrellar margin.

Adult medusae of Cunina octonaria McCrady.
Marginal lobe of Cunina octonaria McCrady with otoporpae (arrows).
